438
00:27:32,776 --> 00:27:34,319
No.

439
00:27:34,403 --> 00:27:37,364
- Entonces...
- Dormimos juntos antes de la boda.

440
00:27:38,156 --> 00:27:41,827
El bebé de Jun-ho está aquí.

441
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:49,251
Cuídate bien

442
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:52,129
